{"tid":599483,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[弱撚智，鬼唔撚知] C.朗拿度：不會再有第二個C.朗拿度","createTime":"2018-03-20T12:37:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T11:15:57.000Z","uid":54373,"like":8,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ef6db3e1421d677ba6976c1051f36e84e75ea69b","tid":599483,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T12:37:02.000Z","msg":"2018年03月18日10:01<br />\n<br />\n　　近日，C.朗拿度在出席自己的新球鞋記者會時，接受了NIKE的採訪，他在採訪中回憶了自己的成為超級巨星的心路歷程，並表示世界上不會再有第二個C.朗拿度。<br />\n<br />\n　　「一開始我夢想著自己能夠成為世界上最好的球員，而我的朋友都那樣看著我，就好像在說&lsquo;你在那胡說什麼呢？&rsquo;」<br />\n<br />\n　　「我最開始踢球只是因為這讓我感到快樂，但在曼聯效力時，我發現自己身上有無窮的潛力。當我加盟曼聯時，我發現和我一樣有天賦，並且努力、忘我、並堅守職業道德的人非常少。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「沒有人能夠和我相比較，也不會有人成為第二個C.朗拿度。你會成為你自己，而我也只會做我自己。」"},{"pid":"88502b269dc8d3007dba9a4658502f591a733612","tid":599483,"uid":149494,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T12:38:04.000Z","msg":"球壇只有一個朗拿度"},{"pid":"b8e256e195b0808d5af508067de483323cc43184","tid":599483,"uid":37735,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T12:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/20/204904_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F20%2F204904_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=bd523a38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16deb80955154e55ae9f26e06a55d12da21a6079","tid":599483,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T12:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9430862da8ad4d81723ee74eabe20163623ec70a","tid":599483,"uid":993,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"88502b269dc8d3007dba9a4658502f591a733612","tid":599483,"uid":149494,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T12:38:04.000Z","msg":"球壇只有一個朗拿度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T12:58:40.000Z","msg":"冇錯，就係牙朗"},{"pid":"eb4842b1d0cb78ddf66ca2a77e0f1e3a939